Helpful email management tools:

- [Smartr](https://www.xobni.com/download/gmail) - makes your inbox more efficient
- [Rapportive](http://rapportive.com/) - tells you information about your contacts, can use to guess emails
- [Mailgun](http://www.mailgun.com/) - set of APIs that lets you send, receive, track and store email
- [MailChimp](http://mailchimp.com/) - sends out email marketing campaigns, gathers analytics
- [WriteThat.Name](https://writethat.name/) - updates contact information from email signatures (for Gmail)
- [Boomerang](http://www.boomeranggmail.com/) - schedule emails and have them sent back to you if you do not receive a reply
- [Streak](http://www.streak.com/) - content resource management for your inbox